    "noticed an altered distribution of neurons and a reduction of cell number in the hippocampus in a status epilepticus mouse model.",
    "These approaches allowed the assessment of the 3D cytoarchitecture, neuron density, and morphology (Fonseca et al., 2018).",
    "The integration of dendrites and synapses into functional networks is heavily affected by how neocortical neurons are positioned during development (Martineau et al., 2018).",
    "Malpositioned neurons in the cortex cytoarchitecture are called heterotopic neurons (Ishii et al., 2015).",
    "These neurons alone may play a role but do not seem to be sufficient to trigger seizures (Aghakhani et al., 2005)."
